amanhã.

596
00:49:06,344 --> 00:49:07,750
Bom dia.

597
00:49:08,296 --> 00:49:09,726
Com fome?

598
00:49:10,382 --> 00:49:11,793
Cereal.

599
00:49:24,998 --> 00:49:27,558
